subject: World Cup (Skiing)
Alpine Skiing
Skiing
lead_paragraph: Lindsey Vonn withdrew from next week’s World Cup races in Beaver Creek, Colo., on Friday, but she left open the possibility of racing the next week at Lake Louise resort in Canada.
